{
  "id": "gen-showcase-kinetic-bloom",
  "name": "Kinetic Bloom",
  "category": "generative",
  "url": "shaders/gen-showcase-kinetic-bloom.wgsl",
  "description": "Geometric flower mandala with damped harmonic oscillator physics. Each petal is a spring-mass system: ζ from mids, ω₀ from bass, underdamped motion x(t)=e^(-ζω₀t)cos(ωt). Bloom cycles triggered by bass. Temporal feedback, chromatic aberration, and ACES tone mapping.",
